ROW.NAME: 应缴税费表中登记注册类型不符合标准代码数据

ROW.DATDSC: select rownum,t.* from ( select (select swjgjc from CJ_FXJK.DM_GY_SWJG b where a.zgswskfj_dm=b.swjg_dm) zgswj_dm,'' n1,'' n2, (select swjgjc from CJ_FXJK.DM_GY_SWJG b where a.skssswjg_dm=b.swjg_dm) skssswjg_dm, to_char(a.yzpzxh) yzpzxh, a.yzpzmxxh, trim(a.djzclx_dm)||(SELECT djzclxmc FROM CJ_FXJK.DM_DJ_DJZCLX b where a.djzclx_dm=b.djzclx_dm) DJZCLX_DM, to_char(a.djxh) djxh, b.nsrsbh, b.nsrmc from CJ_FXJK.ZS_YJSF A,CJ_FXJK.dj_nsrxx B WHERE A.YZFSRQ BETWEEN DATE '[%DAT1]' AND DATE '[%DAT2]' AND A.DJZCLX_DM NOT IN (SELECT T.DJZCLX_DM FROM CJ_FXJK.DM_DJ_DJZCLX T WHERE T.YXBZ = 'Y' AND T.XYBZ = 'Y') and a.sjgsdq like '14511%' and a.djxh=b.djxh order by a.zgswskfj_dm,a.yzpzxh,a.yzpzmxxh ) t

SELECT (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM HX_ZS.ZS_YJSF@JS3Q A WHERE A.YZFSRQ BETWEEN DATE '[%DAT1]' AND DATE '[%DAT2]' AND A.DJZCLX_DM NOT IN (SELECT T.DJZCLX_DM FROM HX_DM_QG.DM_DJ_DJZCLX@JS3Q T WHERE T.YXBZ = 'Y' AND T.XYBZ = 'Y')) AS GX_FZ, (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM HX_ZS.ZS_YJSF@JS3Q A WHERE A.YZFSRQ BETWEEN DATE '[%DAT1]' AND DATE '[%DAT2]') AS GX_FM, ROUND(((SELECT COUNT(1) FROM HX_ZS.ZS_YJSF@JS3Q A WHERE A.YZFSRQ BETWEEN DATE '[%DAT1]' AND DATE '[%DAT2]' AND A.DJZCLX_DM NOT IN (SELECT T.DJZCLX_DM FROM HX_DM_QG.DM_DJ_DJZCLX@JS3Q T WHERE T.YXBZ = 'Y' AND T.XYBZ = 'Y')) / (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM HX_ZS.ZS_YJSF@JS3Q A WHERE A.YZFSRQ BETWEEN DATE '[%DAT1]' AND DATE '[%DAT2]')) * 100, 2) AS GX_BL,
(SELECT COUNT(1) FROM HX_ZS.ZS_YJSF@JS3Q A WHERE A.YZFSRQ BETWEEN DATE '[%DAT1]' AND DATE '[%DAT2]' and A.SJGSDQ like '14511%' AND A.DJZCLX_DM NOT IN (SELECT T.DJZCLX_DM FROM HX_DM_QG.DM_DJ_DJZCLX@JS3Q T WHERE T.YXBZ = 'Y' AND T.XYBZ = 'Y')) AS HZ_FZ, (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM HX_ZS.ZS_YJSF@JS3Q A WHERE A.YZFSRQ BETWEEN DATE '[%DAT1]' AND DATE '[%DAT2]' and A.SJGSDQ like '14511%') AS HZ_FM, ROUND(((SELECT COUNT(1) FROM HX_ZS.ZS_YJSF@JS3Q A WHERE A.YZFSRQ BETWEEN DATE '[%DAT1]' AND DATE '[%DAT2]' and A.SJGSDQ like '14511%' AND A.DJZCLX_DM NOT IN (SELECT T.DJZCLX_DM FROM HX_DM_QG.DM_DJ_DJZCLX@JS3Q T WHERE T.YXBZ = 'Y' AND T.XYBZ = 'Y')) / (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM HX_ZS.ZS_YJSF@JS3Q A WHERE A.YZFSRQ BETWEEN DATE '[%DAT1]' AND DATE '[%DAT2]' and A.SJGSDQ like '14511%')) * 100, 2) AS HZ_BL FROM DUAL
